item.title: CVE-2023-29053|2023-04-11T09:03:07.730Z -- siemens -- jt%20open
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in JT Open (All versions < V11.3.2.0), JT Utilities (All versions < V13.3.0.0). The affected applications contain an out of bounds read past the end of an allocated structure while parsing specially crafted JT files. This could allow an attacker to execute code in the context of the current process.
